item.title: Self Stuffs
item.description: Hi! I’m JotaroKujo0525, you can call me by my real name, Rain Andrew. I’m a 14 year old programmer, i just program whatever the hell i want. I code discord bots, websites and etc. I started as a programmer when a friend in discord told me about these things called discord bots, ye the first thing i programmed was discord bots. The process is excruciating but the output is so satisfying.
